Administration & Permissions 

Recovering Your Login Address
Lost your special login URL? Don't worry, you can get a reminder.

As mentioned earlier, every account on HR Partner has its own unique login URL that you need to type into the address bar of your browser.

If for some reason you forget or misplace your login link, then you can go to the Resend Page https://app.hrpartner.io/user/resend on HR Partner and enter your email address.



You will shortly get an email with your unique company login link for HR Partner and you should be able to log in immediately.

Last updated on July 21, 2020